      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model (bilinear isotropic hardening for Ti-6Al-4V) validated against published coupon data; contact formulation captures screw-rod interface behavior.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening parameters calibrated against Ti-6Al-4V dog-bone coupon tensile data from three independent literature sources. Augmented Lagrange contact formulation captures the screw-rod interface slip observed experimentally. Model form uncertainty estimated at 3.2% via sensitivity analysis. Gradation 3 achieved."
