      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa) and yield strength (880 MPa) sourced from mill certificates for the specific Ti-6Al-4V bar stock used in fabrication. Screw and rod geometry captured by CMM with ±5 µm accuracy. Monte Carlo propagation (N=500) yielded combined input uncertainty of 2.8% on stiffness QoI. Gradation 3 achieved."
