      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from a single production lot of non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws with full material traceability. All 11 specimens dimensionally inspected by CMM prior to testing. Sample representativeness of the production population confirmed. Gradation 3 achieved."
