      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably matched to test article measurements; equivalency table documented.",
      "rationale": "A formal equivalency table maps each simulation input parameter to its experimental counterpart with traceability to CMM records and material certificates. Friction coefficient (µ = 0.15) validated against dedicated screw-rod interface friction tests. All 14 input parameters verified equivalent. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
