      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E/uval) computed for all three QoIs; all values < 1.96; graphical overlay of force-displacement curves provided.",
      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.31), and force at 40 mm (1.78). All three within the pre-specified 1.96 acceptance bound. Force-displacement curve overlays for all 11 specimens show consistent agreement throughout the elastic and early plastic regimes. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
