      "rationale": "The ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol is the FDA-recognized consensus standard for pedicle screw construct evaluation. The validation activity is identical in scope and configuration to the regulatory submission requirement. The FEA model is used to augment, not replace, physical testing. Validation relevance to the COU is maximal. Gradation 3 achieved."
